00:47:08,330 --> 00:47:10,048
Quel chagrin j'ai

712
00:47:10,130 --> 00:47:12,121
Oh, Zazu, reprends-toi.

713
00:47:12,210 --> 00:47:15,247
Chante quelque chose
qui me remonte le moral.

714
00:47:15,330 --> 00:47:19,005
